{"tid":1144122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬，巴塞，馬體會，三隊都俾人反CAP","createTime":"2019-05-08T02:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T21:12:47.000Z","uid":43785,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4d0933681130532ee7df388b3b19bb39005a49","tid":1144122,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皇馬輸ON9輕敵，殘陣出戰。<br />\n<br />\n馬體會輸陰公，輸比球王戴帽<br />\n<br />\n巴塞輸乜野？<br />\n成隊養精打利記，利記殘陣，<br />\n入波主力出唔到<br />\n贏三球在手。巴塞有心踢幾時有輸過四球？<br />\n我真係唔撚明，球王美斯是但入一球都做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n輸四球出局，我真係睇到呆左。"},{"pid":"ecd103d06b23329e950702a0ae3249f43522c6b8","tid":1144122,"uid":43785,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfXxu6m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfXxu6m.gif&h=81058b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好心痛"},{"pid":"74a079c963f6d0398c97da52a2290496e88d585f","tid":1144122,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6tsQ1c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6tsQ1c9.jpg&h=ee5ee019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解會咁架"},{"pid":"134df6425062af6421e3b1b81e23f9680115774c","tid":1144122,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />西甲好慘"},{"pid":"05f09e19c4b6054aa5156170cedc361f68661535","tid":1144122,"uid":249170,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:52:14.000Z"